{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_11_01",
  "title": "佐伯遙子",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ十月かぁ……\n時が経つのは早いわね",
      "startTime": 3.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5000,
          "startTime": 5.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます、遙子さん\nぼーっとカレンダーを見て、どうかしたんですか？",
      "startTime": 9.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、{user}君\n実は、麻奈ちゃんのことを思い出していたの",
      "startTime": 14.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ、麻奈ちゃんのお誕生日でしょう？\n今年はどうお祝いしようかなって考えていたのよ",
      "startTime": 21.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。確かにそろそろですよね\n今年もちゃんとお祝いしないとだ",
      "startTime": 29.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "みんなに声を掛けて、盛大に……なんてどうかしら？\n麻奈ちゃんも、そっちの方が嬉しいでしょうし",
      "startTime": 37.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いいですね。そういえば、麻奈の誕生日に偶然\n月ストのライブがあるんですよ",
      "startTime": 44.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃にそのことを伝えたら、「お姉ちゃんをお祝いして\nあげたい」って、追加で一曲、歌うことになりました",
      "startTime": 50.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんから麻奈ちゃんへのプレゼント\nっていうことかしら。素敵な歌になりそうね",
      "startTime": 56.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "大好きな琴乃ちゃんや、会場の人達にお祝いして\nもらえたら、麻奈ちゃんもきっと喜ぶと思うわ",
      "startTime": 65.1599372569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。それこそ、盛大なお祝いになりそうです\nあの時、遙子さんが麻奈にしてくれたみたいに",
      "startTime": 73.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "それを言うなら、三枝さんと{user}君と\n私で、だけどね。ふふ、あの時は楽しかったわよね",
      "startTime": 81.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――2017年",
      "startTime": 89.0246955872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 90.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　麻奈ちゃんのバースデーライブがあるの？\nそっか、今年は開催出来るのね",
      "startTime": 95.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はい。まだ本人には伝えていないんですが\n大きめの会場で盛大に開催する予定です",
      "startTime": 103.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃん、ずっとバースデーライブをやりたかった\nみたいだし、きっと喜ぶと思うわ",
      "startTime": 110.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "だから{user}君もバタバタしてたのね\n昨日も遅くまで打ち合わせしていたみたいだし",
      "startTime": 117.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "関係各所への連絡や\n他にもいろいろと決めなきゃいけないことが多くて",
      "startTime": 122.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "今日もこれから、スポンサーへの挨拶回りとか\n会場の下見に行かないといけなくて",
      "startTime": 129.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんと二人だけじゃ大変そうね……\n私に何か手伝えることはない？",
      "startTime": 138.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、アイドルに手伝わせる訳にはいきませんって\nこういうのは、裏方の仕事ですから",
      "startTime": 144.7560432015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、麻奈ちゃんのバースデーライブなんでしょ？\n事務所の仲間としても、友達としても、見過ごせないわ",
      "startTime": 152.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "それに人手が増えれば、より大きなことも出来そうだし\n麻奈ちゃんに、もっと喜んでもらえそうじゃない？",
      "startTime": 162.1999898274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "だから、お願い\n私に手伝えることがあるなら、手伝わせてほしいの",
      "startTime": 167.2999898274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました。実は猫の手も借りたかったので\nその申し出はとても助かります",
      "startTime": 177.0333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、じゃあ決まりね\n三人で麻奈ちゃんのために、頑張りましょう",
      "startTime": 183.4333231608,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6300.000000000011,
          "startTime": 189.7333231608
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 187.6499964396
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 187.6499964396
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それで、これがバースデーライブ当日の\n予定なんですが……",
      "startTime": 191.7333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 193.3333297729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど～。一番の盛り上げどころは、ライブ終盤……\n新曲の前にある、麻奈ちゃんへのサプライズ……ね",
      "startTime": 200.2333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、そこでホールケーキを運んで来る予定ですが……\nええと……ちょっと、地味でしょうか？",
      "startTime": 210.1872715269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 213.8666631062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、いいとは思うんだけど……\nケーキって、去年のライブでも贈ってたな～って……",
      "startTime": 218.3333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですね。バースデーライブではなかったですが\n麻奈の誕生日の日にあったライブで贈りましたね……",
      "startTime": 227.3333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 230.7999964396
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ケーキは定番だから外せないわよね\n麻奈ちゃんの好きな味にするのは当然として……",
      "startTime": 235.7333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 239.8333297729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　せっかく会場も大きいんだし、ケーキもすっごく\n大きいのを用意しない？　麻奈ちゃんが驚くくらいの！",
      "startTime": 244.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 249.3333297729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。シンプルですが、インパクトがありますね\nいいと思います。ただ、準備が間に合うかな……",
      "startTime": 253.5666666667,
